#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktimer; is an application that lets you start an application after a "
"certain amount of time has passed."
msgstr ""
"&ktimer; इति अनुप्रयोगः यः निश्चितसमयस्य व्यतीतस्य अनन्तरं अनुप्रयोगं आरभुं शक्नोति ।"

